commit.message:
Fix sphinx config

`build.os` is now mandatory in `.readthedocs.yml`.

(RTD will not automatically assume that you want the latest ubuntu,
which is a deliberate choice from the devs).

See https://github.com/readthedocs/readthedocs.org/issues/8861#issuecomment-1025568797.
Add test for comment in section names
Fix square brackets not parsed in section names

Update README.rst

Fix broken link to RTD: https://configupdater.readthedocs.io/en/latest/api.html#configupdater.configupdater.ConfigUpdater
